('tm160433', 'Just Go with It', 'MOVIE', 'A plastic surgeon, romancing a much younger schoolteacher, enlists his loyal assistant to pretend to be his soon to be ex-wife, in order to cover up a careless lie. When more lies backfire, the assistant\'s kids become involved, and everyone heads off for a weekend in Hawaii that will change all their lives.', 2011, 'PG-13', 117),
('tm160596', 'Zozo', 'MOVIE', 'A Lebanese boy gets separated from his family during the civil war and ends up in Sweden.', 2005, '', 105),
