('tm178201', 'Sherlock Holmes: A Game of Shadows', 'MOVIE', 'There is a new criminal mastermind at large (Professor Moriarty) and not only is he Holmesâ€™ intellectual equal, but his capacity for evil and lack of conscience may give him an advantage over the  detective.', 2011, 'PG-13', 129),
