('tm184608', 'Texas Chainsaw 3D', 'MOVIE', 'A young woman learns that she has inherited a Texas estate from her deceased grandmother.Â After embarking on a road trip with friends to uncover her roots, she finds she is the sole owner of a lavish, isolated Victorian mansion. But her newfound wealth comes at a price as she stumbles upon a horror that awaits her in the mansionâ€™s dank cellars.', 2013, 'R', 92),
